-- Spain to Raise Sanctions for Social Security Fraud, ABC Reports
-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 2012-04-16T07:04:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-16/spain-to-raise-sanctions-for-social-security-fraud-abc-reports.html
Spanish Labor Minister Fatima Banez
plans to announce in the next few days tougher sanctions for
those defrauding the social security system,  ABC  reported today,
citing unidentified people.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Manuel Baigorri in Madrid at 
